title: Fox Mtb Riders Cam McCaul, Tyler McCaul and Steve Smith Test
description:
We filmed this cool edit while testing the 2012 mtb line in Squamish and the North Shore in B.C., Canada. It was fun to see Steve Smith rip it up with the McCaul brothers in B.C. Enjoy!

Music:
³Fermented and Flailing²

By:
NOFX

Courtesy of:
Fat Wreck Chords
